➜关于设置孝义孙夏口腔诊所的公示
http://www.sohu.com/a/416105597_253235	26853
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/d0f126f8d56a4705ada258a97a4927a7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
